data.text:
About STA

With over 80 years of Catholic Education, Tradition, and Excellence thrive on the campus of St. Thomas Aquinas High School.

Dear God,

Through the intercession of St. Thomas Aquinas, grant us a mind to know you, a heart to seek you, the wisdom to find you and the hope of embracing you. We ask this through Christ our Lord.
